data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_601c838e140c25380069a294e2bda0819089806005b7b0c4d5","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":243,"text":"## Smart Eyewear (Contoso Galaxy Innovations) — overview and features\n\nContoso’s Smart Eyewear product (SmartView Glasses) is positioned as **AR-enabled eyewear** that combines hands-free interaction, capture, and eye-protection features. \n\n### Core features\n- **Augmented Reality (AR) interface:** Displays an AR experience directly through the glasses.   \n- **Voice-controlled AI agent:** Enables hands-free control and assistance via voice commands.   \n- **HD video recording with 3D audio:** Records high-definition video and captures spatial/3D audio for richer playback.   \n- **UV protection and blue light filtering:** Includes lens features aimed at sun (UV) protection and reducing blue light exposure.   \n- **Wireless charging with extended battery life:** Supports wireless charging and is designed for longer use between charges.   \n\n### What the documentation covers (beyond the feature list)\nThe included guide outlines areas such as **product overview/controls, sizing and fit, care and maintenance, a break-in period for adjusting to AR, safety tips, and troubleshooting**. "}

